      "id": "cowork-user-1",
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Prepare a launch brief with evidence, owners, risks, and next steps. Include the source documents and keep every claim traceable. This deliberately long request exercises the official long-message collapse behavior and attachment row without using the Code transcript bubble.",
      "createdAt": "2026-07-10T12:00:00.000Z",
      "raw": {
        "type": "user",
        "uuid": "cowork-user-1",
        "message": {
          "role": "user",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Prepare a launch brief with evidence, owners, risks, and next steps. Include the source documents and keep every claim traceable.\n\nExecutive summary: state the recommendation and measurable outcome.\nDecision log: record each decision, owner, evidence, and date.\nLaunch checklist: list dependencies, readiness gates, and rollback steps.\nStakeholder map: identify approvers, contributors, and informed teams.\nCustomer evidence: connect every claim to a source document.\nRisk register: score likelihood, impact, mitigation, and owner.\nTimeline: show milestones, dependencies, and decision deadlines.\nSuccess metrics: define baselines, targets, and measurement windows.\nOperating plan: explain handoffs, escalation paths, and support coverage.\nOpen questions: separate blockers from follow-up research.\nAppendix: preserve links to the original source material.\nQuality check: flag unsupported claims and conflicting evidence.\nReview packet: make the result easy to scan before opening files.\nNext steps: assign an owner and due date to every action.\n\nThis deliberately long request exercises the official long-message collapse behavior and attachment row without using the Code transcript bubble."
            }
          ],
          "files": [
            {
              "name": "launch-notes.pdf",
              "path": "/Users/apple/Documents/launch-notes.pdf",
              "mimeType": "application/pdf"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
